The paper focuses on visual question answering (QA) tasks, which involve deep image understanding and reasoning. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the limitations of current AI models and proposes a novel LSTM model, indicating that it may also belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Finally, the paper evaluates human performance and uses attention mechanisms, suggesting that it may also belong to the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category.
